<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-the-spot">on the spot</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>当场；在现场：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bullet struck his head and he was killed on the spot.
子弹击中了他的头部，他当场死亡。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police were on the spot within a few minutes.
几分钟内警察就赶到了现场。</p></div></div>